OL,3,CTeachers strikes in Jersey will go
OL,4,Cahead after latest pay offer rejected
OL,6,FA three-day teachers' strike in Jersey
OL,7,Fwill go ahead from Tuesday 12 December
OL,8,Fto Thursday 14 December next week.
OL,10,FIt comes after the NEU voted down the
OL,11,FStates Employment Board's latest pay
OL,12,Foffer.
OL,14,FThe rejected offer would have seen
OL,15,Fteachers' pay rise by 8% from 1
OL,16,FJanuary 2024 and a one-off payment of
OL,17,F#1,000 on the same date.
OL,19,FThe revised deal also included pay
OL,20,Frises in line with inflation for 2025
OL,21,Fand 2026.
